Republican Romney Urges Greater Defense, Naval Spending

-- B y   I n d i r a   A . R .   L a k s h m a n a n
-- 
2011-10-07T15:15:53Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-07/republican-romney-urges-greater-defense-naval-spending.html
Former Massachusetts Governor Mitt
Romney called today for a foreign policy based on greater
American military power, with more troops and ships.  The Republican presidential hopeful, in a speech at the
Citadel in Charleston,  South Carolina , said President  Barack
Obama  has bowed to adversaries and undermined world security.  To contact the reporter on this story:
